This is a Alcohol Concentration Detector.
Materials :
1. Breadboard
2. MQ 135 Alcohol Detector
3. 16-bit LCD display
4. Potentiometer
5. Alarm
6. Bulb
7. Cables
Working : 
The device is used to detect the concentration of alcohol in the vicinity of the sensor.
According to the concentration the device shows if alcohol concentration is acceptable.
Once the concentration exceeds the safe range the alarm and bulb switch on.
